Description:
Cedar Brae Golf Club is a beautiful private golf course located in the scenic Rouge Valley in the north east part of Toronto. Cedar Brae is bordered to the east by Canada’s only Urban National Park and is surrounded by nature and not housing. We are very proud of our award winning golf course and its natural surrounds.

Our goal is a simple one; to adhere to our Mission, Vision and Values which defines our core values.

CEDAR BRAE GOLF CLUB
MISSION, VISION & VALUES

MISSION

Cedar Brae Golf Club exists to provide our members, their families and their guests with golfing enjoyment in a culture which promotes camaraderie and fellowship.

VISION

At Cedar Brae, we provide enjoyable golf experiences for a variety of talents in the picturesque and tranquil setting of the Rouge Park.

More specifically, we provide:
• a premier golf course maintained in excellent condition;
• an excellent clubhouse and amenities;
• high quality service;
• the ability to play a fast round of golf;
• ready access to the tee; 
• a club which prudently builds for the future.

VALUES

At Cedar Brae, we respect:
• the game, its traditions and our Club’s history;
• our fellow members and guests;
• our golf course;
• our staff; 
• Our Club’s property and our unique environment in the Rouge Park, of which we are stewards.

If you are passionate about the game of golf or are looking to improve your game, look no further.
